  content_markup: "<h2>Services</h2>\n\n\
    <p><strong>Public Speaking/Chairing/Facilitating</strong>\n\
    Leslie\xE2\x80\x99s by-words are Think, Create, Communicate and Change. From business &amp; personal ethics, work/life balance, and tools you need to unleash creativity and take charge of your life,  Leslie is passionate public speaker who informs and inspires. She can be booked for keynote addresses, to chair meetings and conduct workshops for all business, professional, educational and community events.</p>\n\n\
    <p><strong>Mentorships</strong>\n\
    Leslie has worked for the Writing Centre for Scholars and Researchers at the University of Melbourne for years and is an experienced writing and career mentor.</p>\n\n\
    <p>Wondering how to write a book proposal, get your voice heard on TV, radio, in the print media or online or decide what you might want to do when grow up? A few hours of personalized attention from Leslie will help focus the mind and get that project off and running.</p>\n\n\
    <p><strong>Copy and Ghost-Writing</strong>\n\
    Need some copy written or edited? Have a story to tell? A speech to give that you&rsquo;re too busy to  write? Leslie can get your website or newsletter, family history, autobiography or wedding/ corporate speech done in no time, and in your distinctive voice. .</p>\n\n\
    <p><strong>Research</strong>\n Leslie has several higher research degrees and 15 years of research employment in the community, business and academic sectors. She can help refine, carry out and report on any research brief.</p>\n\n\
    <p>For more information on these or other services, contact <a href=\"mailto:Leslie@Cannold.com\">Leslie</a></p>\n"
