    the nation\xE2\x80\x99s single women will have the option of becoming mothers\r\n\
    through modern technology.\r\n\
    \r\n\
    The case is set to continue on Friday, with the Judge insisting it be\r\n\
    resolved no later than September 2001.\r\n\
