    McBain decision that the state\xE2\x80\x99s denial of fertility treatments, such as\r\n\
    in vitro fertilization and donor sperm, to single women on the grounds\r\n\
    of their martial status violated Australia\xE2\x80\x99s own Sex Discrimination Act,\r\n\
    as well as international agreements to which Australia is a signatory.\r\n\
    \r\n\
