    relaxed and happy mothers, deny their children the carefree childhood\r\n\
    that is their \xE2\x80\x9Cinalienable right\xE2\x80\x9D. Stay-at-home mothers are castigated\r\n\
    for giving up their professional careers and allowing their kids\xE2\x80\x99 school\r\n\
    lives to take on exaggerated importance, as well as providing a poor\r\n\
    role model to their children by helping them cheat on homework\r\n\
    assignments.\r\n\
    \r\n\
    But it is working mothers who really need to duck for cover. According\r\n\
    to the authors, their reliance on prepared and fast foods coupled with\r\n\
