    increased rates of childhood obesity; their busy lives and\r\n\
    competitiveness causes stressed, depressed and ADHD kids who miss out on\r\n\
    time to \xE2\x80\x9Cgaze at the clouds drifting by, watch a butterfly flit around\r\n\
    the garden or throw pebbles in a pond\xE2\x80\x9D; while their lack of time to\r\n\
    listen to their teenagers increases adolescent drinking and anorexia.\r\n\
    \r\n\
