    about, and what academics need from it, leads to the conclusion that in\r\n\
    the new world of electronic communication the Very Smarts don\xE2\x80\x99t need the\r\n\
    Teleporters any more. What they need are new ways of harnessing in-house\r\n\
    talents to access, disseminate and receive rewards for reporting on\r\n\
    quality research results."
