    of citizens to autonomously choose to live what they define as a good\r\n\
    life, and die what they see as a good death. But Liberal democratic\r\n\
    societies have no obligation to honour the wishes of the incompetent or\r\n\
    the coerced. This is why those opposed to the legal right to die use\r\n\
    language - \xE2\x80\x9Cknocked off\xE2\x80\x9D or \xE2\x80\x9Cput to death\xE2\x80\x9D - that assumes what must be\r\n\
