    seen and done together, you\xE2\x80\x99ve never let me down.\r\n\
    \r\n\
    No one is everything. Love yourself, and seek for those you love what\r\n\
    they seek for themselves. Set your beloved free, and perhaps he\xE2\x80\x99ll soon\r\n\
    come back."
