    Minister refused to shake my hand.\r\n\
    \r\n\
    It was an honest move from an un-stage-managed man, and I didn\xE2\x80\x99t have a\r\n\
    problem with it. He didn\xE2\x80\x99t like me and he let it show. It was as\r\n\
    straight and simple as that.\r\n\
