  whole_day: "1"
  title: "In the Family Way @ The Age Melbourne Writer\xE2\x80\x99s Festival"
  submission_notify_name: 
  submission_intro: 
  content_markup: "<p>Kaz Cooke, Jill Singer, Leslie Cannold and, as participating chair,\n\
    Martien Snellen discuss sex, childbirth and reproduction.</p>\n\n\
    <p>The Age Melbourne Writers\xE2\x80\x99 Festival is one of Australia\xE2\x80\x99s largest and\n\
    highest profile literary events. Taking place in August each year, the\n\
    festival\xE2\x80\x99s aim is to showcase the art and talent of the writer and to\n\
