    However, he (and sadly the government also believes Federal Parliament\n\
    should continue to start the day with the Lord\xE2\x80\x99s Prayer.\n\n\
    ### Women & Climate Change\n\n\
    Abbott believes the \xE2\x80\x9Cargument [on climate change] is absolute crap\xE2\x80\x9D. In\n\
    February this year he make his \xE2\x80\x9Cgreat big new tax\xE2\x80\x9D point about the\n\
    government\xE2\x80\x99s proposed Emissions Trading Scheme (ETS) as follows: \xE2\x80\x9CWhat\n\
